content: The first span of the new Kosciuszko Bridge is now open, making it the first major bridge built in New York City in 53 years. The opening was celebrated with a dazzling light show to music Thursday night. The bridge glowed every color of the rainbow as a heavy fog rolled by during the celebration. (Repost from @grimace_586)

content: The Health and Fitness Expo has officially kicked off at MetLife Stadium! The action-packed event runs Saturday and Sunday from 10 a.m. to 4 p.m. You can check out the fun activities in our Insta story, but wouldn't you rather come see for yourself? Follow the link in our bio for details.
name: NBC New York

content: The 2017 NBC New York and @telemundo47 Health and Fitness Expo kicked off with a bang Saturday. You can see more photos in our Insta story or by following the link in our bio. And, of course, you can always experience #Expo4NY for yourself Sunday from 10 a.m. until 4 p.m. #nbc4ny
